# EC550 repository ignore policy
# Keep the repository lean by ignoring everything by default,
# then explicitly allow the parts we want versioned.
*

# Always keep the ignore file itself in version control.
!.gitignore

# Keep GitHub metadata (workflows, issue templates, etc.) tracked.
!.github/
!.github/**

# Keep the syllabus site for the 2025-2026 cohort and all nested files.
!2025-2026/
!2025-2026/syllabus-site/
!2025-2026/syllabus-site/**
